<sect1 id="LOG">
  <title>LOG</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">LOG<indexterm>
      <primary>LOG</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>LOG function</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>n</emphasis><emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="79.50pt" />

      <colspec colwidth="309.30pt" />

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry>n</entry>

          <entry>O número real que será avaliado.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:</entry>

          <entry>LOG retorna um valor real único.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>A função  <emphasis role="bold">LOG </emphasis> retorna o logaritmo de base 10 do parâmetro.</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting>MyLogPI := LOG(3.14159); //0.49715</programlisting>

  <para>Ver também: <link linkend="EXP">EXP</link>, <link linkend="SQRT">SQRT</link>, <link linkend="POWER">POWER</link>, <link linkend="LN">LN</link></para>
</sect1>
